  - **ID: submit-assignment-button-{assignment_id}** - Type: Button - Submit a pending assignment.  - **ID: back-to-dashboard** - Type: Button - Navigate back to dashboard.

### 7. Submit Assignment Page
- **Page Title**: Submit Assignment
